{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/b1-english-for-developers/learn-present-perfect-while-talking-about-accessibility/task-2","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":[],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"learn-present-perfect-while-talking-about-accessibility","challengeType":19,"description":"","nodules":null,"explanation":"<section id=\"explanation\">\n<p>Vremenski oblik <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Present Perfect Continuous</span> se koristi za opisivanje radnji koje su počele u prošlosti i koje su još uvek u toku. Ovo je kreirano korišćenjem <span class=\"highlighted-text\">has/have been + verb(-ing)</span>.</p>\n</section>","helpCategory":"English","instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Ovaj zadatak nema zvuk. Pročitajte pitanje ispod i izaberite tačan odgovor.</p>\n</section>","fields":{"slug":"/learn/b1-english-for-developers/learn-present-perfect-while-talking-about-accessibility/task-2"},"questions":[{"text":"<p>Koja rečenica pravilno koristi <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Present Perfect Continuous</span>?</p>","answers":[{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Sophie works on the screen reader updates recently.</span></p>","feedback":"<p>Ova rečenica je u vremenu <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Present Simple</span>, nije <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Present Perfect Continuous</span>.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Sophie has been working on the screen reader updates.</span></p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Sophie is working on the screen reader updates.</span></p>","feedback":"<p>Ova rečenica se nalazi u <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Present Continuous</span>, opisujući radnju koja se dešava upravo sada, ne na duži period.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Sophie worked on the screen reader updates last week.</span></p>","feedback":"<p>Ova rečenica se nalazi u <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Past Simple</span>, koja definiše završenu radnju, a ne kontinuiranu.</p>","audioId":null}],"solution":2}],"scene":null,"superBlock":"b1-english-for-developers","tests":[],"title":"Vežba 2","transcript":null,"translationPending":false,"videoId":null,"videoLocaleIds":null}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/b1-english-for-developers/#learn-present-perfect-while-talking-about-accessibility","dashedName":"task-2","certification":"b1-english-for-developers","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"b1-english-for-developers","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"learn-present-perfect-while-talking-about-accessibility","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/b1-english-for-developers/learn-present-perfect-while-talking-about-accessibility/task-3","prevChallengePath":"/learn/b1-english-for-developers/learn-present-perfect-while-talking-about-accessibility/task-1","id":"67164bc464cdc045edaccc5f","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":19,"challengeFiles":[]}},"id":"/learn/b1-english-for-developers/learn-present-perfect-while-talking-about-accessibility/task-2"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}